Maree Cheatham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maree_Cheatham 0 Maree Cheatham (born June 2, 1942) is an American actress. She was credited for much of her career as Marie Cheatham. She is known for her performances on the daytime soap operas Days of Our Lives, Search for Tomorrow and General Hospital. She co-starred as Nona on the 2013–14 Nickelodeon comedy Sam Cat.
